OL,5, An initiative to tackle racism in      
OL,6, policing in England and Wales is itself
OL,7, facing allegations of racism from some 
OL,8, of the ethnic minority staff involved. 
OL,10,FThe Police Race Action Plan was        
OL,11,Flaunched after African-American George 
OL,12,FFloyd was murdered in the US in 2020.  
OL,14,FIt aims to help police build better    
OL,15,Frelationships with black communities.  
OL,17,FHowever, BBC Newsnight has spoken to   
OL,18,Fformer members of staff who said their 
OL,19,Fperspectives were ignored.             
